programme.desc: 為振興夜經濟，當局推出餐飲消費券優惠，但網上申領步驟被指費時，也有市民未能用手機二維碼在食店兌換消費券。港人北上消費遇意外！女事主於深圳某水療中心放鬆期間，因地面濕滑不幸跌倒，導致韌帶撕裂需接受手術。水療中心初時承諾負責其內地醫療費用，及後卻只願賠償一半，且要事主簽署不追究文件。事主大控訴，律師亦評論事件。劉德華、林家棟、彭于晏一同為主演電影宣傳，節目送上首映禮花絮。另有旅行篋抵買情報。

programme.desc: 伯駒與永暉出海，二人糾纏間意外墮海，伯駒失蹤。Bin助永暉編故事暪騙警方，更欲藉此控制永暉，更要把巧芝徹底毀滅……巧芝再次出現，勸永暉要擺脫Bin之控制；另又勸浩然應重新做人，不要再自暴自棄。巧芝欲見明軒，卻無法接近。警方拘捕芝控告殺伯駒，幸得有富幫助保釋外出。國昌再次暈倒入院，令巧芝領悟自己和Bin其實同為一人。美詩的聯盟崩潰解散，曉琳卻不肯罷休，欲以永暉之商業罪證來威脅永暉，永暉卻似看透世情，毫不著緊。巧芝為了不再逃避問題，決定認罪承擔所有罪責。

programme.title: 深夜美食團[粵]
programme.desc: 與好兄弟暢聚大牌檔把酒談天，可謂「男人的浪漫」！主持們齊集長沙灣大牌檔，品嚐「豆腐火腩煲」、「薑蔥鮑魚」、「火焰雞煲」等鑊氣十足的美食。中式火鍋與日本菜之間難以抉擇，何不同時兼享？主持們相約陳家樂到中日料理，大歎日式鐵板燒、「鮑魚鵝掌煲」等，還以「卜卜蜆煲」作湯底「打邊爐」。家樂自言廚藝不精，竟被「番茄炒蛋」難倒？主持們又拜訪李嘉有份打理的台式餐廳，細味傳統古早味美食；飯後還有芋圓甜品，份外滿足！

programme.title: 深夜美食團[粵]

programme.title: Hands Up[粵]

programme.title: 妳不是她#14[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 經歷種種事件，林信不知如何面對夏莉，刻意避開她；夏莉悵惘不安，二人冷戰起來。回到時裝店，夏莉見慧雅有心事，追問下得知慧雅以前曾做私影，拍下不少性感照，男友全發現後便失了聯絡。眾人皆勸林信要珍惜夏莉，不要錯過一段真摯感情。林信心生悔意，趕回家找夏莉；二人相見情深，擁抱纏綿。林信及後無意中發現夏莉的另一部手機，見她似是有意隱瞞，甚感疑惑。待夏莉入睡後，林信偷偷拿出手機一看究竟，發現驚人秘密……

programme.title: 旁觀者#9[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 自如發現沈志勛以操弄女人為樂，欲找出拘捕他的罪證。覓希決心對志勛下殺手，安排約會分散自如注意，並計算好時間，打算殺死志勛及處理屍體後再跟自如約會，怎料出現連番意外……自如對覓希起疑心，更感覺覓希正用志勛操弄女人的手段對待自己，她為逃避心中的不安，吃大量甜食強行關上「高敏感」能力，查案時又喝大量鹽檸水，造成精神狀態失衡而倒下住院。覓希為了自如，決定放棄「鼠尾草殺手」的身份。此時，其藏屍地點被發現……

programme.title: 大灣區美味好玩攻略[粵]
programme.desc: 美儀、麥包轉往佛山，有王敏慈加入「跟隊」。老城區活化後成潮人景點，中藥店「變身」咖啡店、以中式白酒調製雞尾酒的酒吧等，都甚吸引。燒鵝也有研究中心？主打燒鵝的食店，出品做到皮脆、肉嫩又多汁。坐上小型賽車，三主持極速分高下。洞穴式按摩店內，敏慈全身被埋進鹽堆中，感受如何？麥包帶兩位拍檔一秒前赴奈良？佛山的濕地公園亦可餵飼梅花鹿。行逛千燈湖夜市，麥包化身「猛男」沖檸檬茶！置身夢幻餐廳，竟是吃樹葉、木炭？

programme.desc: 到台北遊玩有新玩法！主持梁凱晴帶大家乘坐雙層觀光巴士尋幽探秘，上層設有全球首創的噴水系統，讓旅客於炎夏感受清涼。巴士路經多處景點，包括暗藏秘道設施的圓山飯店。而秘道內還有一條瀡滑梯，作用如何？

programme.title: 台灣潮點圖鑑[粵/普]
programme.desc: 蘇子芸來到由六十年老屋改建而成的火鍋店，享用醃燻豬耳絲和頂級牛肉，還有土雞中的霸主「桂丁雞」，別有一番滋味。

programme.title: 台灣潮點圖鑑[粵/普]
programme.desc: 芋頭置身宜蘭咖啡館，一邊歎手工咖啡，一邊做陶藝創作，寫意之至。

programme.title: RUNNING MAN[韓]
programme.desc: 今集邀請了格鬥選手金東炫、秋成勳、鄭讚成和崔鬥虎作嘉賓與成員們一起進行競賽，在錫和世燦化身成為館長，通過任務來協商年薪，最終館長中經費最少的一人和年薪墊底的選手一同受罰，到底這次的懲罰會是什麼呢？

programme.title: 背包女行[粵/普]
programme.desc: 從台北出發，半小時車程就抵達坪林和石碇。徐子婷先到訪茶園，在優美梯田景緻下品嚐茶油料理。想更了解坪林茶葉的文化，不妨到茶葉博物館，除認識各種台灣茶，館內還有文創商店，售賣各式茶葉製品。尋找茶葉特色小食，老街也是「尋寶」之地。有三十多年饅頭老店人手製作的茶葉口味饅頭，子婷又在茶行品嚐期待已久的鐵觀音雪糕。在150年石板屋改建的茶食藝術空間，品嚐過茶香美食，轉地方認識茶葉手工皂製作過程。

programme.title: 陀地外國人[粵] 及 香港有工業[粵]
programme.desc: 要認識各地文化，最好由舌尖開始。主持們來到智利人Arturo開設的多國菜餐館，裝潢卻猶如居酒屋；他奉上看似巨型握壽司的夏威夷飯糰作見面禮，餡料竟有午餐肉，夠晒Fusion！老闆Arturo深受日本動漫文化薰陶，將東瀛美食文化融和，他又何以紮根香港？再試牛油果醬伴脆餅和肉餡餃子，讓嘉慧回味異鄉溫暖。探訪Arturo之家，參加智利人午後燒烤派對，眾主持更從地道肉食、辣肉腸包，窺探不同地方的燒烤文化。

programme.title: 黃金庭院#10[粵/韓] 及 勞資守法保職安[粵]
programme.desc: 美珠為了參賽，竟讓信任和信愛顧店，奶奶怪她不負責任，堅持要開除她。舜華主動說要替東珠找到媽媽，令Sabrina很不安。俊基和Sabrina的婚禮開始許久後，舜華竟到達現場，還認出了蘭淑，於是通知東珠。

programme.title: 窺心事[粵]
programme.desc: 這集探討「報復型人格」，馮子亮、葉靖儀、蔡景行成為實驗對象。三位嘉賓參與比拼，每次勝出者可於飲品中「加料」，最終勝出次數最少者要喝掉飲品。當比拼結果逐漸明朗，兩男知悉自己不會被罰後，懲罰力道大大提升？某人更看似有虐待傾向？「打手板」是接下來的測試遊戲，每人各有一次進攻與防守的機會，從中可觀察到哪位的報復心最強，有兩人竟然完全沒有「出手」！張博士亦教大家化解報復心態，還稱讚主持邵珮詩是箇中高手？

programme.title: 娛樂新聞報道
programme.desc: 每晚緊貼香港娛樂圈的消息，以至世界各地的影視娛樂新聞，報道藝人最新動態、劇集和電影宣傳、演唱會精華、頒獎禮盛況等，甚至遠赴外地採訪娛樂盛事、追蹤各地影星，專訪觀眾熟悉的歌、影、視紅人，讓大家瞬間掌握影視娛樂圈的動態和最新消息。

programme.title: 大鬧廣昌隆#19[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 大廣從高處墮下，回復正常。小芙蓉和達夫為救廣昌隆冒險回陽間，嚇走運昌和靜儀。小芙蓉和達夫忽然全身發燙，盲婆料天靈在背後作祟。盲婆與天靈鬥法，兩敗俱傷。盲婆回到大廣家，天靈召來大批鬼差捉拿小芙蓉和達夫。

programme.title: 古靈精怪 台灣篇[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 新北巿石門金剛宮供奉逾千神像！暉哥、婭彤、茜佳一站式參拜主神四面佛、各路財神、本命太歲……還上天堂下地獄、甚至蓋印花換禮物？三位真女神更造訪比女僕咖啡店更體貼的店家，由像真度超高的美女矽膠娃娃陪伴進餐、拍照，有何互動體驗？台南鹽水蜂炮慶典以高危聞名世界，每年被炸傷的善信不計其數！十多萬枝爆竹叠成的「炮層」在黑夜中齊發，火花亂舞，Ken帶領芸希和嘟嘟穿上全套保護衣，接受「戰火」洗禮，能否全身而退？

programme.title: 不正常愛情研究所[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 社會對單親爸爸、單親媽媽的觀感有差別？紫恩憶述中學有同學人間蒸發，原來去生B？敏芝、國麟亦各有年輕母親的開心故事。年輕辣媽走過傷痛，重拾精彩人生！27歲汽車模特兒兼從業員Copy，育有一名4歲女兒。回想當初意外懷孕，前任卻不想要小孩，Copy最終誕B。及後與前任經歷多次離合，遭對方暴力對待、搶女，令她出現精神問題，更試過輕生。入住精神病院後逐漸重投社會，她還鼓起勇氣找昔日情敵攤開對談，並徹底釋懷。

programme.title: 九尾狐傳#9[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 李硯將計就計，破除了李朗的恐懼，協助智雅脫離困境，同時救出兩人之外，也找到螭龍所在及消滅了暗鬼…李硯將自己和峨音過去的真相告訴智雅，兩人盡釋前嫌，並向賽倫和在煥坦白李硯的真正身分

programme.title: Professions - Men of Salt
programme.desc: Salar de Uyuni, the world’s largest salt flat, has been the source of livelihood for generations. Though working on a salt flat can be bad for their health, they still stay, go to work every day and use the salt to build houses and make art pieces. So how does it feel when salt is your whole life?

programme.title: Lifestyle - The Wizard of Agarkovo
programme.desc: He is called a Russian ‘Hagrid’. Just like Harry Potter’s friend, Aleksandr Biletsky is a gamekeeper, likes magic creatures, and feels in harmony with nature. RT Documentary visits Aleksandr’s fairy tale village, Agavariya, to find out more about organic living, running a creative workshop for ‘wizards and fairies’ and making ‘Muggle’ money in the middle of nowhere.

programme.title: Meeting with Nature - Aurora Hunters
programme.desc: Best observed in high latitudes, the Northern Lights have been fascinating people for centuries. A group of enthusiasts from St. Petersburg, known as the Aurora Hunters, has mastered the art of chasing and predicting them. Natalya, the group’s leader and mastermind, has created a website packed with statistics and forecasts invaluable for everyone who fancies spending a chilly night in the middle of nowhere staring at the sky.

programme.title: Human Rights - Girl Power: Hindi Style
programme.desc: Women in India still have little or no rights and are frequently abused and raped by their husbands. So Sampat Pal, an activist and a local hero, created the Gulabi Gang, which welcomes women in difficult situations and offers them protection and assistance in solving their family problems.

programme.title: Society - Volunteers for Victory
programme.desc: Some Russian men have volunteered to join the fight against Ukrainian nationalists. The documentary tells the stories of four Russian men who felt they couldn’t just stand aside. Some have combat experience others have never served. Could a 60-year-old become a volunteer? Why are regular office workers willing to go to the front?

programme.title: Lifestyle - Tundra Wonder Mums
programme.desc: Pavla Nikolaevna is a ‘chumworker’, a housewife in the tundra.

programme.title: Personalities - Danceducation
programme.desc: Percy Sackey is a Ghanaian primary school teacher who uses dance to build relationships with his pupils and get them to learn better. RTD goes to school with Ghana’s dancing teacher and sees how this dance god uses one of his country’s cultural traditions to get them to enjoy school and learn lessons they’ll never forget.

programme.title: Discovering Russia - Iceline. Lifeline
programme.desc: In 2022 two brand-new Russian icebreakers will operate on the Northern sea route. These ships can break through ice 118 inches thick, need no refuelling for decades, and travel at sea and along rivers. They opened a new era of Arctic sea economy — now there is a direct path between Northern Europe and Asia, bypassing all European seaports. What new opportunities can it bring?

programme.title: Society - 2052 See the Future
programme.desc: Eye-tracking, artificial intelligence, clinical neurotechnologies, virtual reality — all of these have already entered our daily life. Professors from the Higher School of Economics present brand-new inventions and technologies they have produced and explain how they can be effectively integrated in people's life.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - A Tale Of Two Births - Newborn Russia (E8)
programme.desc: Elena and Ekaterina are first-time mums to be. Elena gives birth to baby Jamilla after a routine delivery, but things don’t go quite so smoothly for Ekaterina. At the moment of birth, her baby faces a problem and has to be kept in isolation for a little while. Not long after Elena gives birth, husband Samir, and mother Lyudmila get to meet the newest member of the family.

programme.title: Personalities - Ivan and the Wolf
programme.desc: When Ivan was offered a wolf cub, he immediately agreed, partly out of curiosity but also to save an animal that would otherwise have been put down. The wolf has lived with Ivan, his daughter and two dogs ever since, and soon became a part of the family, as well as regularly attracting media attention. As Ivan’s primaeval pet grows ever bigger, it demands more time, care and space. An RTD crew visits Ivan’s ‘pack’ to find out more about living with a wild predator. As we tag along, we ask if it’s possible to turn a wolf into a pet or whether the call of the wild is too strong.

programme.title: Notes from an american in donbass
Traditions - Mexican Boom Town
programme.desc: Life in Tultepec revolves around pyrotechnics. Producing hand-made fireworks is a passion, an art form, and a source of livelihood for most residents of this Mexican town. But it’s also an extremely dangerous and unpredictable occupation, as those orphaned or widowed by fiery accidents will attest. Meet those willing to risk their lives for their explosive craft as RTD visits Tultepec’s annual pyrotechnics festival.

programme.title: Religion - Father Zosima: Testament of a Donetsk Seer
programme.desc: Elder Zosima foresaw the war in Ukraine and the resurgence of fascism. The monastery he founded is intentionally targeted by the Ukrainian army today. programme.title: Military and War - The Frontline Grind

programme.title: Meeting with Nature - A Bear's Tale
programme.desc: Can a wild bear be a pet? After an ordinary working day at an airfield, Andrey and his colleagues noticed a very young bear running loose. programme.title: Sport - Freeze Divers
programme.desc: Freediving is a challenge in itself: diving into the deep, pitch-black abyss on a single breath, enduring water pressure and keeping a deeply calm state of mind to stay in control while diving. programme.title: Professions - War Correspondents
programme.desc: In the spring of 2022, Pavel Kukushkin volunteered to travel to Donbass as he sought unbiased assessments of the unfolding events. “Many reporters come, film a report, and leave as fast as they can.
